      .col-lg-12.text-center
        %h2.section-heading Services
        %h3.section-subheading.text-muted Yes, we do a lot of stuff.
    .row.text-center
      .col-md-4
        %span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.fa-inverse
          %i.fa.fa-building-o.fa-stack-1x.text-primary
        %h4.service-heading Interior and Landscape Design
        %p.service-subheading We create souls for spaces.
      .col-md-4
        %span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.fa-inverse
          %i.fa.fa-paint-brush.fa-stack-1x.text-primary
        %h4.service-heading Furniture and Product Design
        %p.service-subheading We build almost anything, and sometimes for no reason.
      .col-md-4
        %span.fa-stack.fa-4x
          %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.fa-inverse
          %i.fa.fa-laptop.fa-stack-1x.text-primary
        %h4.service-heading Web Design
        %p.service-subheading We design with passion and deliver value.
